WEBVTT

00:07.040 --> 00:09.520
THE ORIGIN OF ALL BEGINNINGS

00:09.600 --> 00:10.880
This is my uncle's.

00:11.920 --> 00:13.400
It's also a token
between Your Majesty and him.

00:14.520 --> 00:15.360
He held it

00:17.520 --> 00:19.080
in his hand until he died.

00:20.480 --> 00:21.840
If there's truth behind this,

00:22.640 --> 00:24.000
Your Majesty, please investigate it!

00:42.640 --> 00:43.560
Mei Sun,

00:44.160 --> 00:45.600
I still remember that
during our school days,

00:45.680 --> 00:47.360
the imperial teacher
was so strict with me…

00:47.440 --> 00:48.320
YOUNG EMPEROR, YOUNG DUKE OF DING

00:48.400 --> 00:49.480
…while you had all the freedom.

00:52.520 --> 00:54.000
There was one time

00:54.080 --> 00:55.960
when I told you to secretly
take me out of the palace.

00:56.040 --> 00:58.760
My father was furious and
you were imprisoned for several days.

00:59.640 --> 01:02.880
You were always
very protective of me back then.

01:04.599 --> 01:06.160
Back then, the ideas were yours

01:06.240 --> 01:07.640
while I handled the punishments.

01:08.480 --> 01:10.880
Time passed in the blink of an eye.

01:13.040 --> 01:14.960
Your Majesty, you're
the leader of the country now.

01:15.040 --> 01:17.320
It is my duty to serve
the country and the emperor.

01:21.320 --> 01:22.360
Mei Sun.

01:24.200 --> 01:27.200
I am lucky to have you.

01:32.560 --> 01:33.400
Look over there!

01:34.000 --> 01:35.240
Once we get the northern land,

01:35.800 --> 01:37.480
you and I will go there
to watch the sunrise.

01:37.560 --> 01:39.560
But we've not appeased
the pirates in the southeast yet.

01:39.640 --> 01:40.720
I don't have time for the north.

01:41.320 --> 01:43.000
But if I take over the north,

01:43.080 --> 01:45.080
even if you don't fear me
overshadowing your achievements,

01:45.880 --> 01:48.280
I'm afraid you will
say that I deceive you.

01:48.360 --> 01:49.600
Stop doing this.

01:50.560 --> 01:52.040
When we were in the Eastern Palace,

01:52.120 --> 01:55.240
the imperial teacher used this ruler
to teach me how to be an emperor.

01:55.320 --> 01:56.600
Now that the imperial teacher
has passed away,

01:57.200 --> 01:59.880
if I do something foolish in the future,

01:59.960 --> 02:02.200
I have to rely on you to beat me.

02:03.120 --> 02:04.200
Jiang Mei Sun!

02:04.280 --> 02:05.280
Yes, Your Majesty.

02:05.360 --> 02:08.240
You're exempted from the death sentence,

02:08.320 --> 02:09.639
you're allowed to carry a sword around me,

02:09.720 --> 02:10.680
and you need not bow to me.

02:10.759 --> 02:13.320
We're not masters and servants,

02:13.400 --> 02:15.200
so you're not going to
deceive the emperor.

02:17.480 --> 02:19.280
So, Your Majesty, if you make mistakes,

02:19.360 --> 02:21.600
I will not be merciful.

02:24.000 --> 02:24.880
My uncle said

02:25.440 --> 02:27.160
his biggest wish in life

02:27.240 --> 02:28.840
was to defeat the pirates
as soon as possible

02:29.560 --> 02:30.400
and return to the capital

02:31.920 --> 02:33.400
to have a nice chat with Your Majesty.

02:34.680 --> 02:37.800
He has been saying this for 15 years.

02:38.480 --> 02:39.480
It has never changed.

02:41.920 --> 02:43.040
But Your Majesty,

02:44.680 --> 02:46.680
when did your mind start to change?

02:48.760 --> 02:51.320
Or should I say that the emperor

02:52.760 --> 02:54.640
doesn't trust anyone?

02:55.280 --> 02:56.200
How dare you!

02:56.760 --> 02:57.600
Your Majesty.

02:57.680 --> 02:59.320
GRAND HIGH MYSTIC HALL

02:59.400 --> 03:00.480
Your Majesty.

03:02.240 --> 03:03.080
Investigate this.

03:05.840 --> 03:07.280
Find out who punished him.

03:08.640 --> 03:10.480
Find out who harmed Mei Sun.

03:13.040 --> 03:13.880
Your Majesty.

03:15.080 --> 03:17.800
Don't let anyone go!

03:18.640 --> 03:19.880
Your Majesty!

03:19.960 --> 03:24.480
Your Majesty!

03:25.080 --> 03:26.080
Hurry up! Your Majesty!

03:26.160 --> 03:27.720
Tell Mr. Lu to come now!

03:27.800 --> 03:28.760
Your Majesty!

03:29.440 --> 03:32.440
Arrest this treacherous
and unscrupulous man!

03:33.040 --> 03:33.960
Yes!

04:55.840 --> 04:59.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

05:04.160 --> 05:05.040
Mother!

05:05.640 --> 05:06.560
Bring it here.

05:16.760 --> 05:17.880
How is she?

05:21.240 --> 05:23.040
-You may go.
-Go now.

05:23.760 --> 05:24.600
Go.

05:36.520 --> 05:39.880
I went to see those higher officials.

05:40.440 --> 05:43.160
Fortunately, His Majesty is awake.

05:43.240 --> 05:45.480
Otherwise, our family

05:45.560 --> 05:48.560
wouldn't be here now.

05:49.360 --> 05:50.680
What about the imperial court?

05:51.520 --> 05:53.080
What did the Grand Secretariat say?

05:55.920 --> 05:57.240
I can bear with it.

05:58.280 --> 05:59.600
All right.

05:59.680 --> 06:00.720
Don't be angry.

06:01.400 --> 06:04.560
Some plead for mercy
for the Duke of Ding and Yan Tang.

06:04.640 --> 06:06.760
But some mentioned that

06:06.840 --> 06:08.440
although the Duke of Ding is dead,

06:08.520 --> 06:10.280
his army is still around.

06:10.800 --> 06:14.440
Yan Tang has become
the heart of the Duke of Ding's Army.

06:14.520 --> 06:17.960
He even dared to break into
the palace to rebuke His Majesty.

06:18.520 --> 06:21.560
What if he hates the imperial court
and starts an army to cause chaos?

06:25.240 --> 06:26.480
They said if they remove the roots,

06:27.480 --> 06:29.520
they'll be in big trouble.

06:33.040 --> 06:36.040
Fortunately, even though
His Majesty is awake,

06:36.120 --> 06:39.960
he never mentioned Yan Tang's conviction.

06:40.960 --> 06:46.240
We can only bet on
His Majesty's thoughts then.

06:49.400 --> 06:50.760
Candied fruit.

06:51.680 --> 06:52.520
Candied fruit.

06:58.560 --> 06:59.400
Here.

07:04.120 --> 07:07.040
Why isn't the new prescription working?

07:10.720 --> 07:11.880
Servants!

07:11.960 --> 07:14.560
Prepare Mrs. Song's medicine again!

07:22.360 --> 07:25.360
Those at Futing know
the news of the Grand General's death now.

07:26.040 --> 07:28.880
If something happens to Mr. Song,
the army will be in turmoil.

07:30.400 --> 07:32.760
Dou Shi Shu and his men have
impeached Mr. Song for several days.

07:32.840 --> 07:34.640
If anything happens to Mr. Song,

07:34.720 --> 07:36.280
I'm going to bury all the Dous!

07:39.160 --> 07:41.280
General Yan,
we shouldn't be staying here now.

07:41.840 --> 07:42.680
Come with me to the capital.

07:43.520 --> 07:44.600
Let's bring our brothers
from the Duke of Ding's Army.

07:45.240 --> 07:46.680
Even if we have to break into the prison,

07:46.760 --> 07:47.920
we can save Mr. Song.

07:49.680 --> 07:51.080
Mr. Song has not been convicted.

07:51.160 --> 07:52.400
If you do so,

07:53.160 --> 07:54.280
you're rebelling.

07:55.600 --> 07:57.000
If you manage to save him,

07:57.080 --> 07:58.880
hundreds of lives from
the Jiang and Song families

07:58.960 --> 08:01.000
will be lost.

08:01.800 --> 08:03.240
Mr. Song is imprisoned

08:03.320 --> 08:05.960
because of your words!

08:06.480 --> 08:07.600
How dare you stop us!

08:10.800 --> 08:12.120
PICTURESQUE

08:12.200 --> 08:14.320
He broke into the palace, scolded
the emperor and broke the imperial bow.

08:14.400 --> 08:17.000
According to the law,
he should be sentenced to death.

08:17.600 --> 08:18.880
However, the emperor hasn't convicted him.

08:18.960 --> 08:21.240
The Grand Secretariat has been
deliberating for days with no results.

08:22.480 --> 08:24.400
General Yan, what do you think?

08:31.000 --> 08:33.640
His Majesty knows that
the Grand General died unjustly.

08:33.720 --> 08:35.559
He's using this opportunity,
accusing Mr. Song,

08:36.200 --> 08:37.880
to find out the officials' stance on this.

08:37.960 --> 08:39.240
This is one of them.

08:39.320 --> 08:40.840
As long as the emperor feels guilty

08:41.960 --> 08:43.760
and with the continuous exchange
from the officials,

08:44.640 --> 08:46.640
the chief of the Grand Secretariat
and Wang Xing Yi will deal with it.

08:47.920 --> 08:48.760
What about the second reason?

08:48.840 --> 08:51.000
No matter how much
the emperor thinks of the Duke of Ding,

08:51.600 --> 08:53.160
the duke is dead and can't be resurrected.

08:53.240 --> 08:55.200
But Song Mo, who is alive,
is the variable.

08:55.800 --> 08:57.600
If you save him from the prison,

08:57.680 --> 08:59.040
then you're turning the loyal

08:59.120 --> 09:01.720
and handsome young general
in His Majesty's heart

09:01.800 --> 09:04.240
into a rebellious official full of hate.

09:07.280 --> 09:08.960
His Majesty has sent someone
from the Directorate of Ceremonial

09:09.640 --> 09:11.920
to Futing to investigate
the death of the Duke of Ding.

09:13.200 --> 09:16.560
Not even Mr. Gu knows of this.

09:17.280 --> 09:18.680
How did you know about this?

09:19.720 --> 09:21.920
You've been here for several days.

09:22.560 --> 09:25.280
You should know that
my business isn't just in Futing.

09:25.960 --> 09:28.400
There are also regular customers
who are senior officials in the capital.

09:28.480 --> 09:30.960
I have ways to find out the news.

09:32.560 --> 09:35.800
Of course, I hope that you will help us.

09:36.920 --> 09:37.760
How about this?

09:38.680 --> 09:39.760
Let's make a deal.

09:40.600 --> 09:42.520
Come with us to the capital
to rescue Mr. Song.

09:43.520 --> 09:45.120
If Mr. Song is released safely,

09:46.080 --> 09:48.080
we will return Chen Qu Shui to you.

09:49.520 --> 09:53.320
Otherwise, Mr. Chen
will leave this world with me.

09:54.680 --> 09:56.200
I won't be alone then.

09:56.280 --> 09:58.080
No! This is too dangerous.

09:58.160 --> 09:59.160
Yes, it is dangerous.

10:00.080 --> 10:02.320
Young Lady Zhao
values friendship and justice.

10:02.400 --> 10:05.360
She won't let Chen Qu Shui to die with us.

10:07.920 --> 10:09.000
We're allies.

10:10.520 --> 10:13.200
It is my honor to save Mr. Song.

10:14.560 --> 10:17.400
But General Yan,
you actually threatened me.

10:18.520 --> 10:20.120
That's a different story then.

10:23.560 --> 10:26.440
I am a brutish warrior.

10:27.240 --> 10:28.280
My words and actions are harsh.

10:29.240 --> 10:33.080
Young Lady Zhao, since we're allies,
please save Mr. Song.

10:35.400 --> 10:38.560
Young Lady Zhao, please save Mr. Song!

10:42.560 --> 10:44.960
Mr. Yan, your request is granted.

10:47.480 --> 10:53.720
ZHAOWEN BOOKSTORE

10:53.800 --> 10:55.480
My lady, he threatened you with Mr. Chen.

10:55.560 --> 10:56.600
He's not being a gentleman.

10:56.680 --> 10:58.000
Besides, this is so risky.

10:58.080 --> 10:59.920
Well, I don't want Mr. Song to die either.

11:01.200 --> 11:02.040
STORE OWNER OF ZHAOWEN BOOKSTORE

11:02.120 --> 11:03.480
-My lady.
-Mr. Zhao.

11:03.560 --> 11:04.600
I came without notice.

11:04.680 --> 11:06.000
I've prepared everything that's needed.

11:06.080 --> 11:07.280
But there are things we must wait for.

11:07.360 --> 11:09.880
-We'll get them in a day or two.
-It's just a few bookstores.

11:09.960 --> 11:11.600
But they make it look like
they can get all the news.

11:12.240 --> 11:14.680
General Yan,
this is about Mr. Song's life.

11:16.440 --> 11:17.320
General Yan, please.

11:55.560 --> 11:56.920
These will be delivered
to the Directorate of Ceremonial.

11:57.640 --> 11:59.520
The profit is small,
but the quantity is large.

12:02.040 --> 12:03.800
The most profitable one
is the waste papers.

12:04.400 --> 12:05.560
My lady, that was a good idea.

12:05.640 --> 12:07.400
We went to the residences
in the capital to collect waste paper.

12:07.480 --> 12:08.560
After rolling and pounding them,

12:08.640 --> 12:10.440
we turn them into
toilet paper and sell them.

12:11.000 --> 12:11.960
For better quality,

12:12.040 --> 12:13.440
we'll add lime and essential oils

12:13.520 --> 12:14.720
and send it to the Paper-Making Bureau
in the palace.

12:14.800 --> 12:15.640
PERMIT FOR BORDER PASSAGE

12:15.720 --> 12:19.440
In this way, the news from the palace,
harem, the ministries and bureaus,

12:19.520 --> 12:20.400
whether large or small stores,

12:21.120 --> 12:23.920
is connected to a network.

12:27.400 --> 12:30.000
It turns out you have been producing paper

12:31.680 --> 12:33.080
for the entire town.

12:33.760 --> 12:35.520
These are not the keys to the matter.

12:36.400 --> 12:37.960
General Yan, please come with me.

12:45.200 --> 12:46.200
The green vine paper?

12:46.280 --> 12:48.000
It's just an ordinary paper.

12:51.720 --> 12:55.440
Today, only the emperor and the Grand
Secretariat use the green vine paper.

12:56.880 --> 12:58.240
It's to write the scriptures
for prayer sessions.

12:59.920 --> 13:02.920
Your business actually
includes the imperial court.

13:04.680 --> 13:05.640
Well, I'm running a business.

13:06.280 --> 13:08.200
The most important thing
is to treat each other with sincerity.

13:08.840 --> 13:11.640
Only when we know our ability
can we talk about trust.

13:20.040 --> 13:21.680
Several imperial physicians
who treated His Majesty

13:21.760 --> 13:23.560
went home last night.
His Majesty is fine.

13:25.240 --> 13:27.280
The officials and the Grand Secretariat
have been discussing for days.

13:28.360 --> 13:30.760
But His Majesty has yet to
issue an order to convict.

13:32.040 --> 13:34.760
If I could get a hint of
His Majesty's action at this moment,

13:35.400 --> 13:36.320
that would be good.

13:36.400 --> 13:38.560
So you want us to wait

13:38.640 --> 13:40.360
and ignore Mr. Song.

13:41.040 --> 13:43.240
You've been following Mr. Song
for more than ten years.

13:44.400 --> 13:46.520
He is not one
to sit still and wait for death,

13:46.600 --> 13:48.120
or to lack strategy.

13:48.200 --> 13:49.400
Before he broke into the palace,

13:49.480 --> 13:51.360
he must have figured out
a way to break the situation.

13:52.400 --> 13:53.640
In my opinion,

13:54.240 --> 13:56.520
His Majesty,
who fell ill and is recovering,

13:56.600 --> 13:57.920
hasn't convicted Song Mo.

13:58.520 --> 14:00.080
This shows that His Majesty
is reluctant to kill him.

14:00.920 --> 14:03.440
There will be news
from the palace within three days.

14:04.800 --> 14:06.840
So please wait for another three days.

14:06.920 --> 14:08.000
That's the imperial prison.

14:09.040 --> 14:10.600
Those who killed the Grand General

14:10.680 --> 14:13.280
will definitely find ways
to make Mr. Song die in prison.

14:13.360 --> 14:16.200
I've thought of a way
and told Su Lan to do it.

14:17.280 --> 14:18.320
Just wait patiently.

14:23.680 --> 14:26.200
IMPERIAL PRISON

14:26.280 --> 14:27.520
All right.

14:34.200 --> 14:37.600
You're committing a capital crime.

14:38.280 --> 14:39.800
From the officials' point of view,

14:40.440 --> 14:42.400
uncle and nephew are of the same mind.

14:42.960 --> 14:45.160
It's hard to escape
the suspicion of treason.

14:46.760 --> 14:49.000
General Song, just write a confession.

14:49.080 --> 14:52.400
Go soft with His Majesty
and admit your mistake.

14:53.120 --> 14:55.160
At least you can beg for mercy.

14:56.840 --> 14:57.960
Am I right?

15:01.680 --> 15:04.040
Humans have 720 acupoints

15:04.920 --> 15:06.720
and 78 joints.

15:08.320 --> 15:10.280
He doesn't even know
where it hurts the most.

15:11.560 --> 15:12.400
Eunuch Wang,

15:13.080 --> 15:15.440
do you want me to teach your man?

15:18.400 --> 15:19.240
All right.

15:29.320 --> 15:32.560
It seems that
it is useless for me to talk more.

15:34.000 --> 15:36.160
I guess we need something serious.

15:38.760 --> 15:40.280
This is not a big deal.

15:40.360 --> 15:41.920
Why should I be imprisoned?

15:47.560 --> 15:50.400
Eunuch Wang, you're punishing him.

15:51.680 --> 15:52.800
Sorry to bother you.

15:52.880 --> 15:53.720
Please continue.

15:54.640 --> 15:56.760
I'll just watch. Don't bother me.

16:01.680 --> 16:03.720
Mr. Gu, you're…

16:07.640 --> 16:08.640
Look at this.

16:09.400 --> 16:11.760
The Court of Judicial Review
just approved this.

16:11.840 --> 16:14.320
They want to imprison me.

16:14.400 --> 16:15.400
There's nothing I can do.

16:16.440 --> 16:18.840
Song Mo rebelled.
No doubt he'll be sentenced to death.

16:19.440 --> 16:22.560
Do you want to die with him too?

16:23.160 --> 16:24.600
I'm happy to.

16:25.120 --> 16:26.440
You won't let me go to jail?

16:27.280 --> 16:28.680
You don't even follow the rules now.

16:29.800 --> 16:31.640
All right, let's talk about it
in front of my aunt.

16:35.080 --> 16:36.440
As long as you're happy with it.

16:46.120 --> 16:47.120
Open the door!

16:58.160 --> 17:00.840
How dare those servants beat you hard?

17:02.040 --> 17:03.320
Fortunately, I brought medicine with me.

17:03.920 --> 17:05.599
Where's the medicine? Bring it in!

17:07.560 --> 17:08.400
His Majesty…

17:09.680 --> 17:10.800
How is he?

17:14.359 --> 17:15.520
He was conscious the day before yesterday.

17:15.599 --> 17:16.800
But he needs more rest.

17:18.119 --> 17:19.160
I wanted to see His Majesty.

17:20.520 --> 17:21.839
But I was kicked out by my aunt.

17:22.680 --> 17:24.640
Mr. Wu and the others went too,
but they didn't get to see His Majesty.

17:24.720 --> 17:27.400
Even the Crown Prince who went
to take care of him was scolded.

17:31.120 --> 17:32.760
How did you get in?

17:34.080 --> 17:34.920
It was easy.

17:35.440 --> 17:36.720
I found someone who didn't look good

17:37.280 --> 17:38.240
and beat him up.

17:47.560 --> 17:49.120
Which scoundrel beat me?

17:50.680 --> 17:51.520
Me.

17:55.400 --> 17:56.720
You're out of your mind.

17:57.240 --> 17:58.960
You're not as clear-minded
as that female teacher of yours.

18:00.520 --> 18:01.440
A female teacher?

18:02.840 --> 18:05.000
Are you referring to Young Lady Zhao?

18:05.600 --> 18:06.560
Did she tell you to come?

18:07.080 --> 18:09.080
That's right.
Otherwise, I wouldn't be here.

18:09.160 --> 18:11.280
I wander around
the Qianqing Palace like a headless fly.

18:11.960 --> 18:13.160
My aunt avoids me and refuses to see me.

18:13.240 --> 18:15.480
Aunt Min, Song Mo
didn't intend to be disrespectful.

18:15.560 --> 18:16.920
He was just being filial.

18:17.000 --> 18:18.400
-Please spare him, Aunt Min.
-Take him away.

18:18.480 --> 18:20.640
Aunt Min! I promise he won't
do it again! Aunt Min!

18:21.320 --> 18:23.000
Fortunately, a eunuch
from the Paper-Making Bureau

18:23.080 --> 18:24.200
passed me a pouch.

18:24.920 --> 18:26.320
He said it was given to me
by a girl from a bookstore.

18:27.800 --> 18:28.640
When I saw it,

18:29.280 --> 18:30.680
I knew who came up with this idea.

18:30.760 --> 18:32.200
It's your female teacher.

18:34.320 --> 18:36.160
She told you to go to the Court of
Judicial Review to get the document

18:36.240 --> 18:37.360
so that you'll be imprisoned.

18:38.280 --> 18:39.120
That's right.

18:39.760 --> 18:40.920
If I'm here,

18:41.440 --> 18:43.120
no one has the guts to hurt you.

18:47.320 --> 18:50.840
Look. She is such a top embroiderer.

18:52.120 --> 18:53.320
How dare she send the pouch out?

18:59.120 --> 19:01.920
That's a very nice embroidery.

19:02.520 --> 19:04.880
Tell me. What is this?

19:10.440 --> 19:12.440
She's mocking me.

19:13.760 --> 19:15.560
Most of the officials from
the imperial court want you dead.

19:16.600 --> 19:18.480
But she told the eunuch from
the Paper-Making Bureau to deliver this.

19:18.560 --> 19:20.400
She was risking her life.

19:21.720 --> 19:22.880
She helped you to this extent.

19:23.480 --> 19:24.440
She must be chivalrous.

19:28.240 --> 19:32.360
ZHAOWEN BOOKSTORE

19:33.160 --> 19:34.000
Eunuch.

19:34.720 --> 19:35.600
This…

19:36.400 --> 19:37.240
Keep it.

19:41.480 --> 19:44.280
Never do this again.

19:44.360 --> 19:45.800
His Majesty has only met

19:45.880 --> 19:47.280
Mr. Wu and a few officials
from the Grand Secretariat

19:47.360 --> 19:48.880
in the past two days.

19:49.400 --> 19:52.240
At other times, besides immersing
himself in writing the scriptures,

19:52.320 --> 19:54.400
He stares at the ruler
and looks absent-minded.

19:55.160 --> 19:57.800
As for the rest, it's hard for me to tell.

19:59.800 --> 20:00.920
Thank you so much.

20:01.000 --> 20:01.840
You're welcome.

20:07.760 --> 20:08.920
My lady.

20:21.320 --> 20:23.320
The enemy is in the dark.
We can't wait any longer.

20:26.160 --> 20:28.760
I've got my men in ambush around
the Criminal Investigation Service.

20:29.440 --> 20:31.160
Fireworks as the signal, at 11 p.m.

20:32.560 --> 20:33.400
General Yan,

20:34.240 --> 20:35.400
please wait one more day.

20:35.480 --> 20:37.680
We've been waiting for three days.
Do we still have to wait?

20:38.440 --> 20:41.360
Could it be that your idea is to delay us?

20:43.360 --> 20:44.840
The tide has turned.

20:45.720 --> 20:46.760
It's a desperate situation now.

20:46.840 --> 20:48.080
We can't wait any longer.

20:48.160 --> 20:49.080
We must save Mr. Song.

20:49.160 --> 20:50.960
You're sending Mr. Song to hell.

20:51.040 --> 20:52.520
-You fool!
-What did you say?

20:52.600 --> 20:53.800
I'm saying you're foolish!

20:53.880 --> 20:54.920
-You…
-Enough.

20:55.000 --> 20:56.840
Since you want to save Mr. Song,

20:57.960 --> 20:59.360
I'll show you something then.

21:07.840 --> 21:09.160
Don't move!

21:09.760 --> 21:11.760
Dou Zhao! What are you doing?

21:11.840 --> 21:13.720
I'm tired. I don't want to
speak to you again.

21:13.800 --> 21:15.000
Lock them up in the coal house.

21:15.080 --> 21:16.440
-You…
-Dou Zhao!

21:16.520 --> 21:17.640
I'm sorry, guys.

21:17.720 --> 21:18.560
Move!

21:20.080 --> 21:22.320
-Hurry up!
-Go!

21:28.160 --> 21:29.360
You're in charge of the Ministry of Rites.

21:29.440 --> 21:31.520
You should be in the Grand Secretariat.

21:32.560 --> 21:35.800
But Mr. Wu thinks that
you're still inexperienced.

21:37.160 --> 21:40.080
After all, the Grand Secretariat
is headed by him.

21:42.160 --> 21:43.480
Be considerate, all right?

21:45.960 --> 21:48.120
I have not done any merits,
so it's hard to convince people.

21:48.840 --> 21:50.800
Mr. Wu is wise.

21:50.880 --> 21:52.000
What he said is true.

21:54.160 --> 21:55.880
Princess Shude said

21:56.400 --> 21:58.560
you're a brilliant man
with a lot of talent.

21:58.640 --> 21:59.840
I will definitely use your service.

22:00.920 --> 22:02.280
For example, at this juncture,

22:03.000 --> 22:05.320
Song Mo is imprisoned
and awaiting conviction.

22:06.320 --> 22:07.960
All the ministries,

22:08.040 --> 22:09.560
including your disciples,

22:09.640 --> 22:12.960
send the memorials every day
to ask that Song be punished.

22:13.840 --> 22:15.120
What do you think?

22:22.280 --> 22:24.560
Song Mo is a good general.

22:24.640 --> 22:25.600
He's conducted military exploits.

22:26.200 --> 22:28.400
Among the younger generation,
no one can match him.

22:29.640 --> 22:32.400
If this pillar of
the imperial court is killed,

22:32.480 --> 22:33.600
it will disappoint the army.

22:34.400 --> 22:36.440
But the Duke of Ding's Army

22:36.520 --> 22:38.200
has been stationed in Futing
for a long time.

22:38.280 --> 22:40.360
They're not bound by the imperial court
and used to having it their way.

22:40.960 --> 22:43.200
They also left the military camp
without an edict

22:43.280 --> 22:45.320
and even came to the capital.

22:53.640 --> 22:54.960
I'm trying to say that

22:56.040 --> 22:58.800
even though
Song Mo was being disrespectful,

22:58.880 --> 23:00.720
he might have been instigated
by his subordinates.

23:07.280 --> 23:08.640
To get rid of him is dangerous.

23:08.720 --> 23:10.360
Let's punish him lightly for now.

23:11.000 --> 23:13.320
You'll handle this.

23:15.640 --> 23:17.240
Yes, Your Majesty.

23:20.240 --> 23:24.480
"Below is the edict from the emperor."

23:24.560 --> 23:26.720
"On this beautiful day,

23:26.800 --> 23:29.040
the reigning title
will be changed to Fengming."

23:29.680 --> 23:30.800
"A special amnesty is granted

23:30.880 --> 23:33.160
to Song Mo,
the eldest son of the Duke of Ying,

23:33.240 --> 23:36.360
and the Count of Yunyang, Gu Yu."

23:36.440 --> 23:39.840
"Song Mo's positions
in the army will be removed."

23:40.560 --> 23:43.280
"I hope you have reflected
on your mistakes."

23:43.360 --> 23:45.240
"That is all."

24:00.000 --> 24:01.720
Eunuch Wang, why is it a special amnesty?

24:03.920 --> 24:06.000
Mr. Gu, you don't know
about it yet, right?

24:06.520 --> 24:08.800
Today, there was a prayer session.

24:08.880 --> 24:10.400
His Majesty has changed
the reigning title to Fengming

24:10.480 --> 24:11.560
and granted amnesty to everyone,

24:12.200 --> 24:14.600
hence the special amnesty.

24:16.400 --> 24:17.920
What about the grievances
of the Duke of Ding

24:18.640 --> 24:20.840
and the lives of the Jiang clan?

24:22.600 --> 24:25.480
The Jiang clan
is exempted from the death penalty

24:25.560 --> 24:26.640
and demoted to common people.

24:26.720 --> 24:28.600
Men will be exiled to Tieling Militia Unit

24:28.680 --> 24:31.560
while women and children
will be sent to their homelands.

24:32.160 --> 24:34.680
His Majesty is being benevolent.

24:34.760 --> 24:37.920
Mr. Song, go home and recuperate.

24:50.160 --> 24:51.200
You're granted amnesty.

24:51.280 --> 24:53.000
I guess your parents
will come and pick you up.

24:54.600 --> 24:55.440
Mr. Song.

24:55.520 --> 24:56.960
DUKE OF YING'S OLD BUTLER, LU ZHENG

24:57.040 --> 24:58.440
It is inconvenient
for the Duke of Ying to come.

24:58.520 --> 25:01.080
Mr. Song, please return home quickly.

25:03.960 --> 25:06.240
Tell my parents
that I'll go back on my own.

25:08.160 --> 25:09.040
Yes.

25:16.400 --> 25:19.400
I've become a disgrace
to the Duke of Ying.

25:20.120 --> 25:21.360
I should keep a low profile.

25:32.000 --> 25:33.360
This is General Yan's secret code.

25:35.240 --> 25:37.600
This secret code almost
sent you to the underworld.

25:38.240 --> 25:39.640
But consider this as the fireworks

25:40.400 --> 25:41.680
to celebrate your release.

25:45.520 --> 25:46.360
Where is she?

25:47.160 --> 25:49.640
Mr. Song, this way, please.

26:09.960 --> 26:12.560
How did you know
I would be pardoned and released?

26:13.160 --> 26:14.480
News from the Paper-Making Bureau.

26:15.840 --> 26:18.040
His Majesty wrote
the scriptures day and night

26:18.120 --> 26:19.360
and prayed all the time.

26:19.440 --> 26:21.720
He also put the half of the ruler
in front of his desk.

26:22.480 --> 26:25.200
It showed that His Majesty's repentance
overrode his suspicion

26:25.280 --> 26:26.960
about the death of the Duke of Ding.

26:27.600 --> 26:28.880
So he won't kill you.

26:30.720 --> 26:32.200
But why today?

26:32.920 --> 26:35.360
That's because today is
the seventh day after my uncle's death.

26:38.200 --> 26:40.200
Dou Shi Shu and his disciples

26:40.280 --> 26:41.880
impeached every day.

26:42.680 --> 26:43.880
But you used this pouch
and told Gu Yu to protect me.

26:45.480 --> 26:47.280
Why is that?

26:47.880 --> 26:49.680
This is my deal with Mr. Yan.

26:50.520 --> 26:52.240
Since you're safe,

26:52.320 --> 26:54.320
please close the deal as soon as possible.

27:07.040 --> 27:10.120
I've ordered someone
to release Mr. Yan and the others.

27:10.880 --> 27:12.960
I hope you will keep your promise

27:13.040 --> 27:14.680
and return Mr. Chen to me.

27:23.080 --> 27:24.080
Just because of this,

27:26.120 --> 27:27.320
you went against your uncle?

27:40.000 --> 27:42.920
The same fireworks have various colors.

27:44.160 --> 27:46.600
He and I are different.

27:53.640 --> 27:54.480
Thank you.

27:56.800 --> 27:57.640
What did you say?

27:58.480 --> 27:59.360
I didn't hear clearly.

28:05.840 --> 28:06.680
I said…

28:08.720 --> 28:09.560
Thank you.

28:12.440 --> 28:13.600
The fireworks are too loud.

28:13.680 --> 28:15.120
I still can't hear clearly.

28:15.200 --> 28:17.560
Please tell me one more time.

28:17.640 --> 28:18.720
I heard clearly.

28:18.800 --> 28:21.560
-He said he likes you.
-Shut up!

28:25.920 --> 28:27.040
He heard it wrong.

28:27.120 --> 28:27.960
Yes, I heard it wrong.

28:28.040 --> 28:29.880
He said he wants to marry you!

28:31.760 --> 28:32.960
Shut up! Don't talk nonsense!

28:33.840 --> 28:35.200
I'll go home and wait for your good news.

28:50.800 --> 28:52.480
I can't thank you enough
for your kindness.

28:52.560 --> 28:54.760
I will host a banquet at
Guanghe Restaurant the night after.

28:54.840 --> 28:56.200
I hope you will be there.

28:57.200 --> 28:59.920
I'll return Mr. Chen to you on that day.

29:18.760 --> 29:19.760
Mr. Song!

29:19.840 --> 29:20.920
Mr. Song!

29:22.080 --> 29:23.720
-Mr. Song!
-Mr. Song!

29:25.760 --> 29:28.080
You… What's wrong with you?

29:30.040 --> 29:32.720
Well, we were worried about you.

29:32.800 --> 29:34.400
We wanted to break into
the prison and save you.

29:34.480 --> 29:36.080
But Young Lady Zhao persuaded us not to.

29:36.160 --> 29:37.920
-Did she persuade us?
-Shut up!

29:41.120 --> 29:43.000
That was my strategy.

29:43.840 --> 29:45.640
I was betting that His Majesty
felt guilty towards the Duke of Ding

29:45.720 --> 29:47.680
and punished the Jiang clan lightly.

29:50.960 --> 29:52.960
Even she could see this through.
Can't you see it?

29:55.640 --> 29:56.880
Yes.

29:56.960 --> 29:57.960
We were reckless.

29:59.880 --> 30:02.400
I'm going back to the camp
to get beaten 20 times.

30:03.000 --> 30:04.640
-Me too.
-Me too.

30:05.720 --> 30:07.560
You were reckless out of concern for me.
Forget it.

30:08.720 --> 30:10.280
No, I should be punished.

30:15.160 --> 30:16.120
Wash your face before going!

30:21.800 --> 30:24.120
It's getting late.
Young Master Han, please go inside.

30:36.560 --> 30:39.120
Mo, look at the wild deer I got for you.

30:39.200 --> 30:41.600
The deer antler is just right for you.

30:47.920 --> 30:48.960
How's Mother's illness?

30:49.640 --> 30:50.800
Father is taking care of her.

31:08.440 --> 31:09.920
You didn't want to be implicated.

31:10.000 --> 31:12.840
But don't forget that
I'm also one of the Jiangs.

31:13.680 --> 31:15.280
I didn't flatter or insult anyone.

31:15.360 --> 31:18.640
It's very lucky that Yan Tang
could survive to this day.

31:18.720 --> 31:21.600
Do you know that many people
are watching this now?

31:21.680 --> 31:25.360
How could you ignore
the safety of the Songs for the Jiangs?

31:26.840 --> 31:27.680
Mo.

31:30.640 --> 31:34.520
Do you want me
to sever ties with the Jiangs?

31:34.600 --> 31:35.640
Give it to me.

31:36.280 --> 31:38.160
I didn't mean that.

31:38.240 --> 31:40.240
It's just that the situation
is not clear now.

31:40.320 --> 31:42.640
We should be careful
with our words and actions.

31:44.880 --> 31:46.120
Come in!

31:52.160 --> 31:53.920
Father, Mother.

31:55.880 --> 31:56.760
I was reckless.

31:58.000 --> 31:59.240
I made you worry about me.

32:02.240 --> 32:05.040
You must change
your insolent and arrogant behavior!

32:05.120 --> 32:06.480
You made your mother anxious.

32:07.160 --> 32:09.160
She hasn't had a peaceful sleep.

32:18.400 --> 32:19.320
Mother.

32:19.400 --> 32:20.240
Mo.

32:21.160 --> 32:22.320
You look haggard.

32:23.920 --> 32:25.480
You…

32:29.280 --> 32:30.320
This…

32:34.080 --> 32:35.200
Let me take a look.

32:37.640 --> 32:39.240
The Jingyi Guards

32:40.520 --> 32:41.840
are cruel.

32:42.440 --> 32:43.680
It's just a show.

32:44.400 --> 32:45.400
Who dares to really hurt me?

32:46.600 --> 32:49.200
I shouldn't have made you worry about me.

32:49.280 --> 32:51.440
But when I looked at Uncle,

32:51.520 --> 32:52.560
that was the only thing I could do.

32:59.120 --> 32:59.960
Mother.

33:03.440 --> 33:04.440
You just came home,

33:04.520 --> 33:06.480
so I shouldn't tell you this.

33:06.560 --> 33:07.880
But I think

33:09.120 --> 33:11.400
it's time for you to
find someone to care for you.

33:17.520 --> 33:18.360
Could it be that

33:19.200 --> 33:20.480
you have someone you like?

33:25.360 --> 33:28.640
Great!

33:46.560 --> 33:47.400
Mother, here.

33:53.720 --> 33:55.240
Tell me what's on your mind.

33:55.320 --> 33:56.760
Is that special someone

33:57.360 --> 33:58.800
Young Lady Zhao?

34:05.000 --> 34:06.360
My lady, you treat Mr. Chen well.

34:06.440 --> 34:08.520
You took such a huge risk
just to get him back.

34:09.280 --> 34:10.960
Not just for Mr. Chen.

34:13.000 --> 34:14.800
Be it Song Mo or the Duke of Ding,

34:15.520 --> 34:17.080
they were treated unfairly.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.120
I wouldn't have meddled in this
had I not known about it.

34:19.880 --> 34:22.360
But since I knew about it,
I couldn't ignore it.

34:23.639 --> 34:24.880
Mother, what were you thinking?

34:25.520 --> 34:27.000
It must be Lu Zheng and Lu Ming

34:27.600 --> 34:30.320
who told you the nonsense.

34:33.040 --> 34:35.199
They were right though.

34:35.960 --> 34:37.960
Young Lady Zhao was willing
to find ways to help you.

34:38.560 --> 34:40.960
She must be a good girl
who understands justice.

34:41.800 --> 34:43.679
It's a pity that
she was born into the Dou family.

34:44.480 --> 34:47.120
She may be taken advantage
by her fifth uncle.

34:48.920 --> 34:49.840
Did you say Uncle Shi Shu
didn't get into the Grand Secretariat

34:49.920 --> 34:51.280
and the chief is still Mr. Wu?

34:52.480 --> 34:54.440
But based on the Record of Truths,

34:55.040 --> 34:56.360
in this year,

34:56.960 --> 34:58.080
Mr. Wu fell ill and resigned.

34:58.160 --> 34:59.040
LOYAL AND VIRTUOUS MINISTER

34:59.120 --> 35:00.400
So Uncle Shi Shu
got into the Grand Secretariat

35:00.480 --> 35:01.600
and gradually came to power.

35:01.680 --> 35:02.880
DOU SHI SHU, CLOUD-CLIMBING TRAVELER

35:02.960 --> 35:05.480
The emperor changed
the reign title to Fengming.

35:05.560 --> 35:07.200
This is something
that's not in the Record of Truths.

35:08.680 --> 35:10.080
Could it be that my suggestions

35:10.160 --> 35:13.760
have changed the direction of this?

35:13.840 --> 35:15.320
Does that mean whatever is going to happen

35:16.160 --> 35:17.480
is unpredictable then?

35:18.600 --> 35:20.440
There's another matter.
It's about Young Master Wu.

35:22.880 --> 35:23.880
What happened to the Wu family?

35:26.520 --> 35:29.000
To cut off contact with the Dou family

35:29.920 --> 35:31.560
and stabilize the Wu family,

35:32.480 --> 35:35.840
Old Mr. Wu wants De Zhen to marry
the sixth lady of the Liang family.

35:37.640 --> 35:40.280
This time, De Zhen has fallen in love.

35:40.960 --> 35:43.040
He only has Young Lady Zhao in his mind.

35:43.120 --> 35:44.360
He doesn't want to marry Liang.

35:44.440 --> 35:46.800
Even if I have no chance to be
with Young Lady Zhao in this life,

35:48.360 --> 35:50.960
I will only love her.
I will not love anyone else.

35:51.880 --> 35:53.480
I can't go against my will
by marrying someone else.

35:57.240 --> 35:58.680
If we don't prune or cut it,

35:59.600 --> 36:01.720
the plant will eventually grow crooked.

36:02.400 --> 36:03.840
If you didn't want to,

36:04.680 --> 36:06.680
would the sky not fall?

36:07.600 --> 36:08.760
If I didn't want to,

36:08.840 --> 36:09.680
PURE AS MOON, FRESH AS PINE WIND

36:09.760 --> 36:13.640
would Mei Sun revive?

36:17.400 --> 36:19.480
Everything else can be discussed,

36:20.160 --> 36:21.560
except this.

36:22.920 --> 36:25.000
You don't have a choice.

36:27.240 --> 36:29.400
De Zhen's father died early.

36:29.480 --> 36:31.000
He has always been filial
to his grandfather.

36:31.720 --> 36:32.600
Why would he…

36:34.360 --> 36:37.040
Looks like he's really fond of her.

36:39.200 --> 36:40.920
The Dou family
is greedy for power and profit.

36:41.520 --> 36:43.360
Is the marriage about love?

36:44.200 --> 36:46.000
De Zhen has a high fever
after getting wet.

36:46.080 --> 36:47.480
He refused to seek treatment.

36:48.360 --> 36:49.640
If something happens to him,

36:50.200 --> 36:51.520
Old Mr. Wu can't bear it.

36:54.200 --> 36:56.960
Dou Shi Shu got what he wanted.

36:57.040 --> 36:59.800
De Zhen and Old Mr. Wu are stubborn.

36:59.880 --> 37:01.120
I will find a way to be the peacemaker.

37:08.720 --> 37:10.440
Mother, take your medicine.

37:16.560 --> 37:18.520
Godfather, I know I made mistakes.

37:19.040 --> 37:20.360
Learn from Mr. Dou.

37:20.440 --> 37:21.560
He observed His Majesty.

37:21.640 --> 37:23.040
He sought benefits
and avoided disadvantages.

37:23.120 --> 37:25.000
-This is the real skill.
-You're right.

37:25.080 --> 37:29.440
Do you think you'll become great
after forcing Song Mo to confess?

37:29.520 --> 37:32.520
Have you ever thought about
what is His Majesty is thinking?

37:32.600 --> 37:33.440
Or the Grand Secretariat's stance?

37:34.680 --> 37:36.080
Whether he is guilty or not,

37:36.160 --> 37:38.000
is it something we can decide?

37:38.720 --> 37:39.680
I understand.

37:41.840 --> 37:46.320
The Jiying Guards have started
the investigation at Futing.

37:47.040 --> 37:48.720
I should go there now.

37:49.720 --> 37:52.360
Before we find any clues
about the Duke of Ding's case,

37:53.360 --> 37:55.600
do not act rashly.

37:55.680 --> 37:56.520
Yes.

38:17.200 --> 38:18.640
Sir, may I know why are you here?

38:21.320 --> 38:22.160
To issue an imperial edict.

38:30.520 --> 38:31.360
For the past few days,

38:31.440 --> 38:32.840
we have had incidents in which

38:32.920 --> 38:35.240
Mr. Wu refuted His Majesty's granting
Mr. Dou to join the Grand Secretariat

38:35.320 --> 38:36.440
ELEGANT AND BEAUTIFUL

38:36.520 --> 38:38.560
and Young Master Wu
refused to get married.

38:39.240 --> 38:40.600
Everyone in the capital knows that

38:40.680 --> 38:42.720
the Wu family and the Dou family
have become enemies.

38:44.240 --> 38:46.920
The lung abscess occurs when a lung
is attacked during cold weather.

38:47.000 --> 38:48.880
De Zhen was caught in the rain
and refused medical treatment.

38:49.880 --> 38:52.200
By the way, has Physician Li
returned to the capital?

38:53.120 --> 38:54.160
He's on his way.

38:54.240 --> 38:55.360
He will likely arrive at night.

38:55.440 --> 38:56.520
All right.

38:59.240 --> 39:01.640
Have you prepared the gifts
based on the list I gave you?

39:02.400 --> 39:03.240
Yes.

39:03.880 --> 39:06.240
But Chen Qu Shui has been staying
in Yizhi Hall for a long time.

39:06.320 --> 39:09.560
I guess he knows everything here.

39:10.720 --> 39:12.160
I don't think it's inappropriate

39:12.240 --> 39:13.240
to release him just like that.

39:15.240 --> 39:16.400
Well, we're not just allies.

39:16.480 --> 39:17.640
She saved my life too.

39:17.720 --> 39:20.120
Since we made a promise,
we can't break it.

39:21.800 --> 39:23.640
Indeed a promise is important.

39:23.720 --> 39:25.760
But I felt that
Young Lady Zhao and Dou Shi Shu

39:25.840 --> 39:27.880
were cooperating.

39:27.960 --> 39:29.640
No sooner had something good happened

39:29.720 --> 39:30.960
than trouble came.

39:31.600 --> 39:33.640
I'm afraid that your ally

39:33.720 --> 39:35.040
can't guard against villains.

39:40.280 --> 39:41.840
Grandpa, stop pressuring me.

39:43.360 --> 39:44.560
Pine and cypress

39:45.640 --> 39:46.880
will grow naturally.

39:49.120 --> 39:50.880
But to beautify them,

39:52.400 --> 39:54.000
you twist the branches

39:55.240 --> 39:56.840
and don't hesitate to
change their growth direction.

39:58.720 --> 39:59.720
Grandpa,

40:00.840 --> 40:02.480
do you treat me as a plant too?

40:03.880 --> 40:06.920
You wanted to train with others,
so I allowed it.

40:08.160 --> 40:09.680
You love woodcrafting,

40:10.480 --> 40:12.080
and I pretended not to know about this.

40:13.000 --> 40:16.800
When the family was stable
and you were willful,

40:16.880 --> 40:18.680
I could still protect you.

40:20.200 --> 40:23.680
But things are different now.

40:25.360 --> 40:27.080
New officials are rising

40:27.720 --> 40:29.760
and I'm surrounded by enemies.

40:31.360 --> 40:32.520
If I'm…

40:35.600 --> 40:37.360
If I'm no longer around,

40:39.760 --> 40:41.560
who will protect you?

40:43.320 --> 40:45.840
Who will protect the Wu family?

40:46.840 --> 40:48.160
You're forcing me!

41:00.680 --> 41:03.040
If you don't like Ms. Liang,

41:04.000 --> 41:06.400
I have several candidates
from other families.

41:07.440 --> 41:08.920
You can choose any.

41:09.840 --> 41:11.720
Except for the daughters
of the Dou family.

41:11.800 --> 41:13.320
Even if you seek death,

41:13.400 --> 41:14.560
I will not agree to it.

41:28.400 --> 41:30.920
This is Physician Li
who is here to treat Young Master Wu.

41:32.800 --> 41:34.600
Please come with me. This way, please.

41:34.680 --> 41:37.360
WU'S RESIDENCE

41:42.800 --> 41:44.480
I'm sorry. Please wait for a while.

41:44.560 --> 41:45.600
She'll be back soon.

41:52.520 --> 41:53.840
The floor is cold.

42:01.320 --> 42:02.160
Grandpa.

42:03.040 --> 42:04.240
Do you think

42:05.520 --> 42:06.800
I refused treatment

42:08.200 --> 42:11.080
because I wanted to force you
to let me marry Young Lady Zhao?

42:13.080 --> 42:14.840
She doesn't love me at all.

42:16.040 --> 42:17.640
I just don't want to accept the fact that

42:18.680 --> 42:20.960
I should get married
to stabilize the family.

42:22.160 --> 42:25.080
I don't want to lie to myself
and hurt others!

42:29.280 --> 42:31.960
I just want to break free
from this prison.

42:33.240 --> 42:35.080
I just want to live my life

42:35.160 --> 42:36.680
without going against my will.
Can't I do that?

42:38.280 --> 42:39.480
Do you take me

42:42.320 --> 42:43.760
for a warden?

42:45.560 --> 42:49.560
Can't you see that I protect you
from the wind and rain every day?

42:49.640 --> 42:52.120
Do you think everything will go well

42:52.200 --> 42:54.560
when you do woodcrafting?

43:13.040 --> 43:16.760
Young Lady Zhao,
can I see you for the fifth time?

43:16.840 --> 43:18.080
Even if you don't change your mind,

43:18.160 --> 43:19.320
I'll still be happy about it.

43:20.000 --> 43:21.080
You lied to me to gain my trust.

43:21.160 --> 43:22.560
You informed
your fifth uncle of the information.

43:22.640 --> 43:24.560
Shouldn't I doubt you?

45:18.080 --> 45:19.400
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM.

45:19.480 --> 45:20.880
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA ARE
FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
